'''新天地耶稣教证据帐幕圣殿'''（{{Kor|漢=新天地예수敎 證據帳幕聖殿|諺=신천지예수교 증거장막성전|f=y}}），簡稱'''新天地教會'''或'''新天地'''，是由[[李万熙|李萬熙]]于1984年3月14日在[[大韩民国|韓國]]创建的[[基督教|基督教]]系[[新興宗教|新興宗教]]团体。至2014年统计，其有超过120,000名信徒<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|title=Controversial religious group holds int'l peace event in Seoul|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/culture/2020/01/293_164816.html|accessdate=2020-01-24|date=2014-09-18|work=koreatimes|language=en|archive-date=2020-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327190426/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/culture/2020/01/293_164816.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；2020年估计，其目前已有大約240,000名信徒<ref>{{Cite news|title=Coronavirus: South Korea to test 200,000 sect members as pandemic fears hit markets|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/feb/25/coronavirus-south-korea-to-test-200000-sect-members-as-pandemic-fears-hit-markets|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2020-02-25|accessdate=2020-02-26|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|first=Martin|last=Farrer|first2=Lorenzo|last2=Tondo|last3=agencies|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225235008/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/feb/25/coronavirus-south-korea-to-test-200000-sect-members-as-pandemic-fears-hit-markets|archive-date=2020-02-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 沿革 ==
新天地教會總會長[[李萬熙|李萬熙]]出生於1931年，現年90歲，曾參與許多韓國具爭議性之基督教復興運動。其中包括在1960年代盛行的橄欖樹運動（Olive Tree movement），與被指控為詐騙的帳幕聖殿運動（Tent Temple movement）。於1970年代復興運動開始沒落之後，興起了新的一批末日論教派，乘著趨勢，李萬熙於1984年3月14日創立新天地教會，總部設在大韓民國[[京畿道|京畿道]][[果川市|果川市]]，<ref>{{Cite web|title=超級傳播者來自「邪教」？韓國的新天地教會究竟是什麼|url=https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5099074|accessdate=|author=張毓思|date=2020-02-21|format=|publisher=天下雜誌|language=|archive-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301004106/https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5099074|dead-url=no}}</ref>教會網站自稱是「神在世上獨一無二的國和聖殿」，並以「如蠟燭般犧牲我們的肉體」來順從耶穌旨意。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/4375585|title=南韓新天地教會什麼來頭？外媒曝：龐大又富裕|author=中央社|date=2020-02-27|work=經濟日報|publisher=經濟日報|accessdate=2020-02-27|language=zh|format=|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112194253/https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/4375585|dead-url=no}}</ref>其自稱為《聖經》中提到之「神應許的牧者」，教會為基督真正的繼承者，教眾多被教導其為耶穌轉世再臨之主，依據聖經內容之暗喻，審判日會在信徒達到十四萬四千人後來臨，教主將帶領教眾進入天堂。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-51580975|title=肺炎疫情：韓國出現新冠病毒群聚性感染事件|author=BBC NEWS|date=2020-02-20|work=BBC|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2020-02-20|language=zh|format=|archive-date=2021-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211009235147/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-51580975|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0"/>

== 組織 ==
新天地組織依據啟示錄第四章內容，教主稱「[[會長|總會長]]」，其他階級有「部長」、「教育長」、「十二支派長」、「長老」，分別再依照職能賦予「講師」、「教師」、「宣教士」、「傳道士」、「執事」、「門徒」等職能。

於地域分布上，將[[大韓民國|大韓民國]]劃分為12個牧區，稱之為十二支派，分別以耶穌的[[使徒_(基督教)|十二門徒]]進行命名，其中最大的支派為[[光州|光州]]的彼得支派與[[大邱|大邱]]的達太支派。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=剖析新天地異端|url=https://ocbf.ca/2012/religion/religions/budda/5488|accessdate=|author=頌天恩|date=|format=|publisher=海外華人福音網|language=|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027201341/http://ocbf.ca/2012/religion/religions/budda/5488|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Zion Christian Mission Center Introduction|url=http://en.shincheonji.kr/?ch=about03_01|accessdate=|author=新天地教會官網|date=|format=|publisher=新天地教會|language=|archive-date=2021-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211023215728/http://en.shincheonji.kr/?ch=about03_01|dead-url=no}}</ref>

所有新入教之教徒，需先經過大約兩個月的一對一聖經輔導，再進入《錫安基督教神學院》學習六個月，最後在學員通過神學院畢業考試之後，才會正式在教會註冊，成為信徒。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2577026/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83%EF%BC%8E%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A5%E6%95%99%E6%80%92%E5%91%8A%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E6%96%B7%E7%B5%95%E4%BE%86%E5%BE%80%20%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0%E5%89%8D%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%92%E7%88%86%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96|title=【新天地教會．韓國疫情】女兒為入教怒告母親斷絕來往 新天地前信徒爆教會神秘文化|author=李凱晴|date=2020-02-28|work=晴報|publisher=晴報|accessdate=2020-02-28|language=zh|format=|archive-date=2020-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228104402/https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2577026/%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259C%2583%25EF%25BC%258E%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%2580%2592%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%2596%25B7%25E7%25B5%2595%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25BE%2580%2520%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25BE%2592%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A7%2598%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 禱告方式 ==
有別於一般基督教會一周一次的[[禮拜|禮拜]]，新天地教會更為頻繁，約有三成的教眾最多一周會有6次緊密接觸活動，據韓國當地媒體指出，信徒中的已婚婦女會群聚在教會大樓，依靠著彼此，並且大聲[[禱告|禱告]]將近半個小時，最後再接受佈道將近一個小時。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://turnnewsapp.com/global/reading/168372.html|title=韓新天地教會 創立以來諸多爭議|author=旺報|date=2020-02-27|work=旺報|publisher=中國時報集團|accessdate=2020-02-27|language=|format=|archive-date=2020-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302093236/https://turnnewsapp.com/global/reading/168372.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=超級傳播者來自「邪教」？韓國的新天地教會究竟是什麼|url=https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5099074|accessdate=2020-02-21|author=張毓思|date=2020-02-21|format=|publisher=天下雜誌|language=|archive-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301004106/https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5099074|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 傳教方式 ==
常以隱密傳教形式，讓被稱為「收割者」（harvester）的教徒潛入其他教會活動，除隱匿新天地信徒身分外，同時向潛在的信徒進行傳教。<ref name=":1" />

==被指邪教==
新天地是一爭議性組織，並被許多團體指控為[[邪教|邪教]]團體<ref name="auto" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Mystery surrounds visit to UAE of alleged religious cult|url=https://www.thenational.ae/uae/mystery-surrounds-visit-to-uae-of-alleged-religious-cult-1.126337|accessdate=2020-01-24|work=The National|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228151928/https://www.thenational.ae/uae/mystery-surrounds-visit-to-uae-of-alleged-religious-cult-1.126337|archive-date=2020-02-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=(Yonhap Feature) Mannam Volunteer Association faces criticism from foreign residents|url=https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20121028000200315|accessdate=2020-01-24|date=2012-10-28|last=이동민|work=Yonhap News Agency|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228185145/https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20121028000200315|archive-date=2020-02-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>或[[基督教|基督教]][[异端|異端]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=剖析新天地異端 {{!}} 海外華人福音網|url=https://www.ocbf.ca/2012/religion/religions/budda/5488|accessdate=2020-01-24|work=www.ocbf.ca|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820045704/http://www.ocbf.ca/2012/religion/religions/budda/5488|archive-date=2019-08-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{NoteTag|惟對於世界上是否有「邪教」這回事，學界尚有爭議，而目前學界傾向認為世界上並沒有「邪教」這回事，而所謂的「邪教」，往往是對評價者所不喜歡的宗教，尤其[[新興宗教|新興宗教]]的主觀性負面評價，詳情可見「[[邪教|邪教]]」一文的說明。}}。具有個人崇拜導向，其信徒相信，李萬熙是[[耶稣|耶稣]]轉世、或為耶稣所派的使者<ref>{{Cite news|title=Churches on alert of "dangerous cult" Shincheonji on takeover mission|url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=11817352|newspaper=NZ Herald|date=2017-04-04|accessdate=2020-01-24|issn=1170-0777|language=en|first=Lincoln Tan Lincoln Tan is the New Zealand Herald’s diversity, ethnic affairs and immigration senior reporter|last=lincoln.tan@nzherald.co.nz @LincolnTanNZH|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126222354/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=11817352|archive-date=2020-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。教會並宣稱，《[[圣经|聖經]]》中充滿著[[隐喻|隱喻]]，只有李萬熙可以看懂和解釋。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Shincheonji members helped believer "escape" family|url=https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=11817395|newspaper=NZ Herald|date=2017-04-04|accessdate=2020-01-24|issn=1170-0777|language=en|first=Lincoln Tan Lincoln Tan is the New Zealand Herald’s diversity, ethnic affairs and immigration senior reporter|last=lincoln.tan@nzherald.co.nz @LincolnTanNZH|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227153529/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=11817395|archive-date=2020-02-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>

李萬熙於創立新天地之前，曾經是宗教團體{{link-en|Olive Tree|Olive Tree (religious movement)}}的成員。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Guwonpa, WMSCOG, and Shincheonji: Three Dynamic Grassroots Groups in Contemporary Korean Christian NRM History|url=https://www.mdpi.com/2077-1444/10/3/212|last=Kim|first=David W.|last2=Bang|first2=Won-il|date=2019/3|journal=Religions|issue=3|doi=10.3390/rel10030212|volume=10|pages=212|language=en|author=|access-date=2020-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816033230/https://www.mdpi.com/2077-1444/10/3/212|archive-date=2019-08-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年11月，[[英格兰教会|英國英格蘭教會]]向约500個教區發出正式警告，要求教會成員警惕新天地教會的附屬組織"Parachristo"的傳教活動。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Exclusive: Churches warned of 'deceptive cult' linked to South Korea infiltrating congregations|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/10/exclusive-churches-warned-deceptive-cult-linked-south-korea/|newspaper=The Telegraph|date=2016-12-10|accessdate=2020-01-24|issn=0307-1235|language=en-GB|first=Harry|last=Farley|first2=John|last2=Bingham|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810145555/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/12/10/exclusive-churches-warned-deceptive-cult-linked-south-korea/|archive-date=2019-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

