2020年2月，新天地教会内发生大規模[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]群聚性感染。第一名新天地教會教徒確診個案「第31號患者」出現於2月18日。<ref>{{Cite news|title=韩国出现新冠病毒群聚性感染事件|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-51580975|newspaper=BBC News 中文|date=2020-02-20|accessdate=2020-02-23|language=zh-Hans|archive-date=2021-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211011005041/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-51580975|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=韩国病例激增至204起 七成在新天地教会感染|url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/international/story20200222-1031044|accessdate=2020-02-23|date=2020-02-22|work=早报|language=zh-Hans|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222195206/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/international/story20200222-1031044|archive-date=2020-02-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至2月20日，在[[大邱廣域市|大邱]]和慶北地區出現的30例中有23人也被發現與新天地教會有關<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://m-cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20200220001600881?section=society/index|title=详讯：韩国新增31例感染新冠肺炎确诊病例 累计82例|date=2020-02-20|accessdate=2021-12-22|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430003319/https://m-cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20200220001600881?section=society%2Findex|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2月28日，韩国1766宗病例中高達80%與這個神秘教會有關，社會對教會的恐懼和仇恨亦越來越多<ref>{{cite web|title='We're treated like criminals': South Korean sect feels coronavirus backlash|publisher=The Guardian|date=2020-02-28|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/feb/28/were-treated-like-criminals-south-korean-sect-feels-coronavirus-backlash|access-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301025341/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/feb/28/were-treated-like-criminals-south-korean-sect-feels-coronavirus-backlash|archive-date=2020-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該教會的感染人數數量眾多，與教會的內部文化有顯著的關係。教會教導信徒不要害怕生病，即便生病也不能停止到其他基督教教會勸說他人皈依「新天地」，教會亦禁止信徒在禱告會戴上[[口罩|口罩]]或眼鏡<ref>{{cite web|title=South Korea's approach to coronavirus COVID-19 could be putting millions at risk and things could be worse if it spreads to the North|publisher=ABC News|date=2020-02-28|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-02-27/south-koreas-relaxed-approach-sparksfears-spread-to-north-korea/12005704|access-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229001352/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-02-27/south-koreas-relaxed-approach-sparksfears-spread-to-north-korea/12005704|archive-date=2020-02-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。信徒往往輕看淡化疫情引起的風險而隱瞞自己的病情<ref>{{cite web|title=【新天地教會．韓國疫情】女兒為入教怒告母親斷絕來往 新天地前信徒爆教會神秘文化|publisher=晴報|date=2020-02-28|url=https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2577026/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83%EF%BC%8E%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A5%E6%95%99%E6%80%92%E5%91%8A%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E6%96%B7%E7%B5%95%E4%BE%86%E5%BE%80%20%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0%E5%89%8D%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%92%E7%88%86%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96|access-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228104402/https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2577026/%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259C%2583%25EF%25BC%258E%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%2580%2592%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%2596%25B7%25E7%25B5%2595%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25BE%2580%2520%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25BE%2592%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A7%2598%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596|archive-date=2020-02-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第31號病例在確診前曾至少兩次拒絕轉院，不願接受嚴重急性呼吸綜合症冠狀病毒2型的檢測。

信徒對自己的身份保密、隱藏行蹤的習慣也導致了傳染控制措施無法順利進行。[[大韓民國政府|大韓民國政府]]在調查初期無法追踪第31例患者行蹤，截至2月27日，第31號病例一起進行禮拜的4,000多名信眾仍有300多人無法取得聯繫。信徒不願揭露身份，也導致公眾無法發現是自己是否已接觸信徒，因而應該進行自我隔離<ref>{{cite web|title=Secretive Church Sect At The Center Of South Korea's Coronavirus Outbreak|publisher=NPR|date=2020-02-24|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/02/24/808914718/secretive-church-sect-at-the-center-of-south-koreas-coronavirus-outbreak|access-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301031539/https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/02/24/808914718/secretive-church-sect-at-the-center-of-south-koreas-coronavirus-outbreak|archive-date=2020-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

時任首爾市長[[朴元淳|朴元淳]]在2020年3月1日以「没有为防止疫情扩散积极采取措施」起訴教區總會長李万熙和12个支会领导嫌疑謀殺及傷害，同時指出教會提供的虛假信息妨礙了衛生當局的工作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202002/29/WS5e5a37fce4b05d1eff0b3b15.html |title=突破3000例，韩国“新天地”教主遭调查 |access-date=2020-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229143701/http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202002/29/WS5e5a37fce4b05d1eff0b3b15.html |archive-date=2020-02-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=【新冠肺炎・韩国】新天地教主李万熙被指“故意过失杀人”｜多维新闻｜全球|url=https://www.dwnews.com/全球/60170665/新冠肺炎韩国新天地教主李万熙被指故意过失杀人|access-date=2021-05-27|date=2020-03-01|last=多维新闻|work=多维新闻|language=zh-Hans|archive-date=2021-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527064515/https://www.dwnews.com/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83/60170665/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0%E6%95%99%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%8E%E4%B8%87%E7%86%99%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%95%85%E6%84%8F%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%B1%E6%9D%80%E4%BA%BA|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Seoul mayor sues South Korea religious group for 'murder' and 'injury' over spike in coronavirus cases|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/02/coronavirus-seoul-mayor-sues-south-korea-shincheonji-religious-group.html|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2020-03-02|last=Choudhury|first=Saheli Roy|work=CNBC|language=en|archive-date=2020-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303035627/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/02/coronavirus-seoul-mayor-sues-south-korea-shincheonji-religious-group.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=韩宗教团体新天地领袖就集体感染谢罪|publisher=韓聯社|date=2020年3月2日|url=https://cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20200302005200881?section=society/index#none|access-date=2021年12月22日|archive-date=2021年11月2日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102192202/https://cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20200302005200881?section=society%2Findex#none|dead-url=no}}</ref>。翌日，李万熙召开记者会，就教内集体感染事件跪地谢罪<ref name=":2" />。他稱「我从没想过会发生这种事…我仍在试图弄明白这怎么会发生」<ref>{{cite web|title=新冠疫情简报：中国新增确诊数降至新低；疫情影响解放军|publisher=纽约时报中文网|date=2020年3月3日|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/morning-brief/20200303/coronavirus-china-briefing/|access-date=2020年3月4日|archive-date=2021年12月15日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215195058/https://cn.nytimes.com/morning-brief/20200303/coronavirus-china-briefing/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=救世主还是邪教头目？揭秘韩国新天地教会创始人李万熙|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20200303/coronavirus-south-korea-shincheonji/|access-date=2021-05-27|date=2020-03-03|last=Sang-Hun2020年3月3日|first=Choe|work=纽约时报中文网|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215200250/https://cn.nytimes.com/asia-pacific/20200303/coronavirus-south-korea-shincheonji/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

3月3日，首尔市政府表示，称将按照程序推进新天地教会法人执照的吊销工作<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.sina.com.cn/c/2020-03-04/doc-iimxyqvz7816624.shtml |title=韩国首尔拟吊销新天地教会法人执照 |access-date=2020-03-04 |archive-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327190428/https://news.sina.com.cn/c/2020-03-04/doc-iimxyqvz7816624.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

